description: Crispy Buffalo Cauliflower with Vegan Blue Cheese Dip! Are you ready for the most delicious vegan bar food you've ever had? These cauliflower buffalo wings are the perfect easy to make treat. There's a secret ingredient in this buffalo cauliflower recipe that makes these super crispy, even though they are baked. Meaning these cauliflower wings are actually pretty healthy for you! I also share with you my recipe for vegan blue cheese dip which is perfect when paired with vegan buffalo cauliflower. I hope you enjoy this recipe!!
name: Vegan Buffalo Cauliflower with Vegan Blue Cheese Dip
